The goal of this project is to build an interactive dashboard using Power BI to:

Analyze sales, profits, and quantity trends

Identify top-performing regions, categories, and sub-categories

Provide actionable business insights for decision-makers

Demonstrate skills in Power BI data modeling, transformation, and visualization

🧰 Tools & Technologies Used:
Power BI Desktop
Power Query Editor
DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
csv as data source

📊 Dataset Overview:

SuperStore Sales Dataset
Contains data related to a retail store’s operations, including:

Order ID, Order Date, Ship Date

Customer Name, Segment, Region

Product Category, Sub-Category

Sales, Quantity, Profit

📈 Key Features in Dashboard:

📅 Date-based filtering (Monthly/Quarterly/Yearly)

📍 Regional performance analysis

📦 Category/Sub-category performance

🚚 Shipping and delivery time insights

📉 Forecasting future sales trends (based on historical data)

🔍 Top N product/category drill-down

